    "In our case, this capability has been translated into the ability of Generative Large Language Models to discover and provide amplified knowledge due to the vastness of the data and information on which they have been trained.",
    "In our case, (b-i) \"Discovering\" identifies the application of AI to conduct an in-depth analysis of visual or textual content to detect meaningful insights.",
    "This process provides designers with valuable information, influencing the creative process at an early decision-making stage.",
    "\"Inspiring\" is the second concept we identified, which is based on a re-interpretation of the \"Visualising\" concept proposed by Shi et al. (2023).",
